      <title>刚果叛军如何取得进展并威胁与卢旺达开战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/how-rebel-advances-in-congo-threaten-another-war-with-rwanda</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国东部地区连年战乱，数百万人流离失所。2025 年初，与卢旺达结盟的叛军包围了刚果一个重要的贸易中心，暴力冲突进一步升级，威胁到这两个中非邻国之间的全面战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/how-rebel-advances-in-congo-threaten-another-war-with-rwanda</guid>
